ZH: 他现在大权在握，可以做出任何决定。
EN: He now holds all the power and can make any decision.

ZH: 总统大权在握，对政府的决定有着决定性的影响。
EN: The president holds all the power and has a decisive influence on government decisions.

ZH: 公司的CEO大权在握，能够左右整个企业的发展方向。
EN: The CEO of the company holds all the power and can influence the direction of the entire enterprise.

ZH: 老板大权在握，员工们都得听从他的安排。
EN: The boss holds all the power and the employees have to follow his arrangements.

ZH: 在这个国家，权力大权在握的人往往能够为所欲为。
EN: In this country, those who hold all the power can often do whatever they want.

ZH: 领导者必须意识到，大权在握也意味着更大的责任。
EN: Leaders must realize that holding all the power also means greater responsibility.

ZH: 只有大权在握的人才能够决定公司的未来发展方向。
EN: Only those who hold all the power can determine the future direction of the company.

ZH: 这位明星凭借着大权在握的地位，影响着数百万粉丝的态度和思想。
EN: This celebrity, with all the power in his hands, influences the attitudes and thoughts of millions of fans.

ZH: 老师在学校里拥有大权在握的地位，能够左右学生的行为和学术发展。
EN: Teachers hold all the power in schools and can influence students' behaviors and academic development.

ZH: 这个国家的领导者大权在握，决定着整个国家的命运。
EN: The leaders of this country hold all the power and determine the fate of the entire nation.

ZH: 司法部门对于司法审判的大权在握是维护法制秩序不可或缺的。
EN: The judiciary's holding all the power in judicial trials is essential for maintaining the rule of law.

ZH: 在这个集团中，董事长大权在握，能够影响公司的各项决策。
EN: In this group, the chairman holds all the power and can influence various decisions of the company.

ZH: 大权在握的领导者需要懂得倾听下属的建议和意见。
EN: Leaders who hold all the power need to listen to the advice and opinions of subordinates.

ZH: 队长大权在握，决定着球队的整体战术和布阵。
EN: The captain holds all the power and determines the overall tactics and formations of the team.

ZH: 拥有大权在握并不意味着可以为所欲为，需要遵守一定的规则和法律。
EN: Having all the power in hand does not mean one can do whatever they want, they need to follow certain rules and laws.

ZH: 这个独裁者大权在握，将整个国家置于他的控制之下。
EN: This dictator holds all the power and places the entire country under his control.

ZH: 董事会主席拥有大权在握，对公司经营的方向有着关键的影响。
EN: The chairman of the board holds all the power and has a crucial influence on the direction of the company's operation.

ZH: 针对危机的处理，总经理拥有大权在握，必须迅速做出决策。
EN: In dealing with crises, the general manager holds all the power and must make decisions quickly.

ZH: 这个社区的领导者大权在握，关乎着上千居民的利益和生活。
EN: The leader of this community holds all the power and affects the interests and lives of thousands of residents.

ZH: 在这个体制中，最高领导人大权在握，掌握着国家的方向和命运。
EN: In this system, the top leader holds all the power and determines the direction and fate of the country.
